nodes.text: The Official Star Wars Fact File Index
The Official Star Wars Fact File Index was the index of The Official Star Wars Fact File. It contained a list of all articles published in the fact file.

It was organized into two sections, the first contained a list of all the articles organized into the six major categories. The second section of the index was organized by alphabet and contained not only all articles, but also references to other articles.
